parameters:
\nc<>(Even when I look at the newspaper in the convenience store,
there are no articles about magical girls,) (And when I ask
people on the street, they don't know about villains. Why!?)

\nc<>(...No, I still can't relax.) (It was definitely close
by.)

\nc<>(I was cornered in a dead-end alley while running away from
the school villain...!)

\nc<>Ah, at that time we didn't know each other yet, right? But
it's okay.
\nc<>If we gradually get to know each other from now on...

\nc<>No, why are you feeling down? This kind of world can't be
real, right?
\nc<>That's right, I was with Reina trying to destroy that...
\nc<>No, don't forget. I was with Reina...
\nc<Hina?>How strange. Why are you resisting so much?
\nc<>Hina-chan... no, it's not! Who are you!

\ncI know your wish. This is a world without magical girls or
villains.

\ncA world where you can live an ordinary life and no one
becomes unhappy because of it.

\ncIsn't this what you've always wished for? Why are you so
resistant?
\nc<>No! I never wished for something like this...!

\nc<>I've been thinking about it for a long time. It would have
been better if there were no villains from the beginning.

\nc<>If that were the case, even if I turned my eyes away from
the battle, I wouldn't have to feel guilty.
\nc<Hina?>Then why? Is it because you can't meet your new friends?

\ncDon't worry. I'm sure we can become good friends. This is
such a convenient world.

\nc<>So, are there any villains in that wonderful world who have
been tormenting me?

\nc...? If that's the case, you won't be able to become happy,
right?

\ncBecause I wished for the villains to disappear. So of
course, they're not here.
\nc<>If I'm here, it should be fun.

\nc<>I don't want to have the painful experience of breaking off
friendships and just want to spend peaceful time with my
friends.
\nc<>I think I can live the ordinary days I wished for.
\nc<>And that's how they ended up living that kind of life.

\ncStop resisting. There is interference from the outside.

If you continue to resist, it cannot be sustained.

\nc<>There are those who believe in me and restrain their
desires.

\nc<>There are citizens who give unwavering support to an
inexperienced me.

\nc<>There are people who believe in me and wait for me to
definitely stand up.
\nc<>Do you think we can just pretend that never happened?!

\nc<>If at the end of the path I have continued to walk while
suffering, there is now...

\ncHuman ideological interference is increasing. Magical power
values are increasing.

\nc<>I won't give up on carrying this burden just because it's
painful!

\nc<>Memory K5: Finally obtained the ability to overcome
temptation.

\nc<>Good listeners increased by 7,000, while bad listeners
increased by 3,000.
